Class Solution

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Solution

  • public class Solution
extends java.lang.Object
    Description of the Solution class
    Used to calculate evidence tables, their correction factor/conflict and to determine the plausibility or belief of this evidence table.
    Author:
    Watnuss
